T*
(growth stages?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Study Tips After Reading) Tj
T*
(- Rewrite the overview of Reproduction in your own words after studying it.) Tj
T*
(- Use short exercises built around reproductive structures and processes before trying) Tj
T*
(harder tasks.) Tj
T*
(- Keep track of mistakes such as mixing fertilization with implantation or growth stages) Tj
T*
(and write the correction beside each one.) Tj
T*
(- Revise Reproduction regularly so the method behind sexual reproduction, fertilization,) Tj
T*
(and development becomes familiar.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Independent Practice) Tj
T*
(- Explain the overview of Reproduction and describe how it fits into Biology.) Tj
T*
